```py
WITH customers(id, total_spend) AS (
    VALUES
    (100, 1583.49),
    (200, 8739.03),
    (300, 431.00),
    (400, 1.00),
    (500, 22.27)
),
reviews(id, customer_id, reported_as_spam) AS (
    VALUES
    (1, 100, False),
    (2, 100, False),
    (3, 400, True),
    (4, 400, True),
    (5, 500, False)
)
...
```

```py
...
SELECT
    c.id,
    c.total_spend,
    COALESCE(COUNT(r.id), 0) AS n_reviews
FROM customers c
LEFT JOIN reviews r
    ON c.id = r.customer_id
WHERE
    NOT r.reported_as_spam
GROUP BY
    1, 2
ORDER BY
    1
```

```py
...
SELECT
    c.id,
    c.total_spend,
    COALESCE(COUNT(r.id), 0) AS n_reviews
FROM customers c
LEFT JOIN reviews r
    ON c.id = r.customer_id
    AND NOT r.reported_as_spam
GROUP BY
    1, 2
ORDER BY
    1
```
